Text: Kigogo anachofanya ni kumkera martin...anasubiria martine aandike maneno mengiii afu yeye anajibu kidogo tu
Yaaan ana sifa mwenzake ana andika insha yeye anajibu inshort  na yanaeleweka
Mbna maandish humu kwngu yame badilika
Siku nikifa naomba nizikwe na iphone yangu
Unatumia neno gani kuomba TENDO (kwichikwichi) kwa mpenzi wako?.
